    {
        "url": "/quotes/chris_renaud_764622",
        "quote": "When I was at Marvel, they were in bankruptcy, which is hard to believe now with 'Avengers 2' out, but it was during the 1990s. It was a troubled place. Comic book sales were dropping. Work was scattered.",
