    {
        "url": "/quotes/chris_renaud_764623",
        "quote": "The great thing about working in comics is that visually, you're the sole voice. You have to figure out the staging, the lighting, the composition, the character emotions, the action. You get a script, but you're trying to work it out in individual panels. It's a terrific exercise in creative thinking and creative problem-solving.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Chris Renaud",
            "url": "/quotes/chris_renaud_764623"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Voice",
                "url": "/topics/voice"
