            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/chris_renaud_764624",
        "quote": "It is so gratifying for me the degree to which the Minions have been embraced. It's almost unprecedented in the CG animated world. It's amazing. That's really all a creator hopes for, that their characters grow beyond them. It's like Darth Vader and Batman. They've gotten bigger than their creators.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Chris Renaud",
            "url": "/quotes/chris_renaud_764624"
        },
